name: Sheep Dip Canyon
description:
Introduction

This is the TRUE Sheep Dip canyon, not to be confused with Twister Canyon that is in a different creek some distance away. Also sometimes called Deathtrap Canyon, which is a different canyon again.

1 abseil, lots of jumps and swims, a really fun canyon.
